1
00:00:02,530 --> 00:00:05,512
[Take Me To The Pilot]

2
00:00:05,512 --> 00:00:11,955
And so I’m flying on Aeroflot
from Deli to Moscow.

3
00:00:12,272 --> 00:00:15,836
The flight attendants
are preparing the passengers.

4
00:00:15,997 --> 00:00:18,850
I’m sitting, 
they’re serving the scene.

5
00:00:18,883 --> 00:00:25,437
I see some people are reading spiritual books, 
they might have acquired on their tour.

6
00:00:25,437 --> 00:00:27,808
And the person sitting next to me
leans over and says,

7
00:00:27,808 --> 00:00:31,368
“I don’t believe in gurus 
or reading books.

8
00:00:33,166 --> 00:00:36,366
I think you create your own reality.

9
00:00:36,366 --> 00:00:40,201
I heard from this one teacher 
actually you don’t need a teacher.

10
00:00:40,201 --> 00:00:43,970
And I read this one book that said, 
“You don’t need to read books.’”

11
00:00:43,970 --> 00:00:45,420
I turned to him and I said,

12
00:00:45,420 --> 00:00:48,742
“How would you feel 
if on the public address 
 

13
00:00:48,742 --> 00:00:53,202
the pilot came on and said 
something like this to the passengers,

14
00:00:53,202 --> 00:00:55,561
‘Ladies and gentlemen,

15
00:00:55,561 --> 00:00:58,561
I’d like to welcome you 
aboard the flight this evening.

16
00:00:58,561 --> 00:01:02,798
I think you might want to know, 
I’ve never flown an aircraft before,

17
00:01:02,798 --> 00:01:05,581
I’ve never undergone 
any sort of training.

18
00:01:05,581 --> 00:01:07,668
I don’t rely upon a navigator.

19
00:01:07,668 --> 00:01:12,034
Actually I believe flying 
is really an intuitive thing.

20
00:01:12,034 --> 00:01:18,503
You just going to trust yourself, 
believe in yourself, and envision your destination.’”

21
00:01:18,503 --> 00:01:21,118
I’d get off the flight immediately.

22
00:01:21,118 --> 00:01:28,589
Arrogance, bravado is the opposite 
of spiritual culture.

23
00:01:29,722 --> 00:01:35,981
So don’t you think it’s even 
more critical choice to make

24
00:01:36,521 --> 00:01:40,281
who’s going 
to pilot your soul?

25
00:01:40,511 --> 00:01:42,264
What was he thinking?!
 

26
00:01:43,795 --> 00:01:45,225
Was he thinking?

